    "This can be seen by using the cloaking property of the dotted line as follows.",
    "For S κ ∈ Bd(Σ), take a ∈ Tube S κ corresponding to an f ∈ C(c ⊗ χ ⊗S κ → χ ⊗S κ ⊗ c) as on the left-hand side of Eq.",
